# Canonical ignore content for the bottling-company-test images.
#
# BUILD CONTEXT = the edgecommons umbrella root (compose sets build.context: ../../..)
# so each image can COPY from the unpublished sibling core/libs/* next to its
# own component repo.
#
# HOW THIS TAKES EFFECT: Docker/BuildKit resolves the ignore file for a build as
# "<dockerfile-path>.dockerignore" first, then falls back to "<context>/.dockerignore".
# Because compose points each service at bottling-company-test/dockerfiles/<img>.Dockerfile,
# an identical copy of THIS file is shipped next to each Dockerfile as
# bottling-company-test/dockerfiles/<img>.Dockerfile.dockerignore (generated from this one),
# so the ignore rules apply WITHOUT placing anything in the umbrella root. (Patterns are
# matched relative to the build-context root regardless of where the ignore file lives.)
# See README "Build context & .dockerignore".
#
# If you prefer a single file, copy this to edgecommons/.dockerignore instead and delete the
# per-Dockerfile copies — but that writes into the umbrella root.

# Rust build output (all repos) — huge. (A Rust build `target/` sits at a crate ROOT.)
**/target/
# ...but the edgecommons TS lib has SOURCE directories literally named `target/` (the
# metric-emission targets log/messaging/prometheus/cloudwatch under src/metrics/target).
# Those live under a `src/` tree, so re-include any `target/` nested under `src/` — a Rust
# build `target/` never is. Without this the console TS build fails with TS2307 "Cannot find
# module './target'". (Last-matching pattern wins in a .dockerignore, so this re-includes
# only src-nested target dirs; crate-root Rust target dirs stay excluded.)
!**/src/**/target/
!**/src/**/target/**

# Node build output / deps — huge
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.astro/

# Java build output
**/*.class

# Python caches / venvs
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/*.egg-info/

# VCS + editor
**/.git/
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/

# The harness's own runtime output (must never enter an image)
bottling-company-test/replicated-output/
bottling-company-test/out/

# The sibling per-component harness — not needed by any build here, and its
# replicated-output/ holds large committed Parquet fixtures.
system-test/

# Umbrella clutter irrelevant to any build
old_readmes/
roadmap/
**/*.log
**/.DS_Store
